**imagine just for a moment**, that every game industry in the world can&#039;t sell anything to Casuals anymore. to survive they can&#039;t dumb down, cut content for later DLC. each new game must bring something new to the table or it will fail and bankrupt the company.

how would the current video games look like in your opinion? 

here&#039;s what I think{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-rainbows}} 



1.WOW would be dead years ago
2. we would have a 10 out of 10 Dragon age 2, that would make Dragon age 1 seem like a &quot;weak game&quot;
3. Destiny would Rival Witcher 3 and win &quot;best game ever made&quot;, 10/10 in every aspect (instead of the piece of shit it was before the last DLC)
